{"title":"献给几内亚友人","authors":["朱子奇"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":1,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"献给几内亚友人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱子奇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几内亚说：不！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢的几内亚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你对“共同体”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愤怒地说：“不！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自主的几内亚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你对颠覆和干涉者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚定地说：“不！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又逼你接受"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马和骑士的共处？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几内亚再次说：“不！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你从不曾答应敌人："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“是。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你总是昂起头回答："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“不！不！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几内亚说不，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"非洲燃起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由之火。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向你祝贺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来，朋友！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们对世上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切霸道和邪恶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都说“不！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再说“不！决不！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红豆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白云海上飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红豆生西非。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我见红豆有无数，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数科纳克里的最美。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颗儿是小小的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壳儿是硬梆梆的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"色彩是红格艳艳的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颗颗红豆呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颗颗几内亚人民的心呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"压不扁，捏不碎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹雨打色不褪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄萨摩里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是英雄萨摩里的土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是鲜血染红的土地！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是英雄萨摩里的儿女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是不畏强暴的儿女！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萨摩里的口号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是我们的誓言："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“不给敌人留下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个老人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗小米，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚壁清野战到底！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，几内亚人民！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们都是今天的萨摩里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我骄傲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是萨摩里的好兄弟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注：萨摩里·杜尔，是十九世纪八十年代领导反殖民主义武装斗争的几内亚民族英雄，他的事迹在西非广泛流传。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}